title: Top Five Christopher Nolan Movies and a ‘Tenet’ Review From Canada
description:
'Tenet' is here! But not everywhere. With Christopher Nolan's latest unavailable to California and New York residents, Sean and Amanda call on Ringer contributor and Canadian citizen Adam Nayman to share a spoiler-free review of the filmmaker's latest journey into bended time and space. Plus: Sean, Amanda, and Adam share their favorite Nolan works and discuss how his films will be remembered.

Hosts: Sean Fennessey and Amanda Dobbins
Guest: Adam Nayman
